{"tid":1911671,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先同女同學傾咗成粒鐘 呢粒鐘係我咁大個仔最美好嘅回憶","createTime":"2020-03-05T13:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T15:38:43.000Z","uid":218575,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a38b7cf5b59586907c5a05b1a7418f1dd1622cdf","tid":1911671,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"話說呢排啲功課開始多 <br />\n無啦啦kayan打咗俾我<br />\n話想同我傾電話<br />\n初頭我好緊張 唔知點開話題<br />\n話曬都第一次同女女傾電話<br />\n可能佢feel到我緊張 <br />\n好主動咁話教佢做功課黎做藉口同我打開話題<br />\n<br />\n佢真係好細心 我講曬啲答案之後<br />\n原本仲想傾耐啲 點知佢話驚我攰<br />\n叫我早啲收線抖下 <br />\n呢一刻我戀愛了 <br />\n天呀 世界上點解會有咗善解人意嘅好女仔<br />\n<br />\n收線之前 佢仲話下份econ功課約定咗我架啦 <br />\n叫我記得聽她電話 <br />\n<br />\n死啦 唔通呢啲就係連登仔口中嘅約會<br />\n唔通我受愛神邱比特嘅眷顧 中咗佢枝箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n期待下一次嘅來電😭"},{"pid":"054a929bb294d41cd931ce7e22e1ab8c769c9cb5","tid":1911671,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"悶"},{"pid":"c5794cc58c355d4541efc096aa48ac1c51782909","tid":1911671,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"6cbf8a09b5fc51d7084400086e1ea0fb61a639e3","tid":1911671,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"054a929bb294d41cd931ce7e22e1ab8c769c9cb5","tid":1911671,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"悶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁唔俾面！"},{"pid":"e8f8dd87509a8c86270b0f55d88b9c5188e385e0","tid":1911671,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5794cc58c355d4541efc096aa48ac1c51782909","tid":1911671,"uid":214997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"0/10"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"真人真事俾0.5都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee86df4d93568a6862a1f5da379e6e377470660","t